---
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-[#2a3f50]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Portrait placeholder with warmth -->
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-[#3d5a6e] relative overflow-hidden max-w-sm">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#2a3f50]/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <!-- Illustrated silhouette -->
        <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2" width="220" height="320" viewBox="0 0 220 320" fill="none">
          <ellipse cx="110" cy="280" rx="90" ry="40" fill="#2a3f50" opacity="0.5"/>
          <rect x="70" y="130" width="80" height="160" rx="4" fill="#f7f3ee" opacity="0.15"/>
          <circle cx="110" cy="90" r="50" fill="#f7f3ee" opacity="0.18"/>
          <rect x="85" y="140" width="50" height="80" rx="2" fill="#b5541c" opacity="0.25"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
          <p class="text-[#f7f3ee] font-medium text-lg" style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;">Tom &amp; Linda Vásquez</p>
          <p class="text-[#9ab0bc] text-sm mt-1">Spokane residents, 22 years</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Accent detail -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#b5541c]/20 -z-10 hidden md:block"></div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-[#b5541c] mb-6">About Gonzaga Rentals</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-light text-[#f7f3ee] leading-snug mb-8" style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;">
        We live here.<br/>
        <em class="italic text-[#ede7dc]">This is our neighborhood too.</em>
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-[#c8d8e0] text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Tom and I started renting properties near Gonzaga after our youngest finished her degree there in 2008. We'd watched too many students land in apartments that were overpriced, poorly maintained, or managed by people who'd never set foot in Spokane. We knew we could do it differently.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every property we own is within walking distance of campus. Every one is inspected, repaired, and ready before a tenant moves in. We don't hand off to property management companies — when you rent from us, you have our personal number.
        </p>
        <p>
          We've housed students, professors, nurses at Sacred Heart, and young families putting down roots. Spokane is worth investing in. We plan to keep doing it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-[#3d5a6e] grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#f7f3ee] font-medium mb-1" style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;">Linda Vásquez</p>
          <p class="text-[#9ab0bc] text-sm">Tenant relations, leases, and everything that keeps the day-to-day running smoothly.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#f7f3ee] font-medium mb-1" style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;">Tom Vásquez</p>
          <p class="text-[#9ab0bc] text-sm">Maintenance, repairs, and a 20-year friendship with every hardware store in East Spokane.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
